response.overview: A dedicated FBI agent recalls the agency's battles against the Klan, organized crime and Communist spies.
response.tagline: You are crouched in a basement stairway opposite a theatre in Chicago. Keep your eyes on that FBI man across the street. He has set the trap for deadly public enemy, John Dillinger...
response.title: The FBI Story
